OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FDespite attempts to diversify their
OL,7,Fbusiness and a recent expansion into
OL,8,FGuernsey, the three companies explain
OL,9,Fthey were unable to raise enough funds
OL,10,Fto overcome "historic and ongoing bad
OL,11,Fdebts".
OL,13,FThey add: "We are absolutely
OL,14,Fdevastated that with the ceasing of
OL,15,Fthe companies, this also involves our
OL,16,F78 employees losing their jobs and
OL,17,Flivelihoods which in itself is
OL,18,Fheartbreaking.
