OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,F"We understand that this news will
OL,7,Fcome as a shock and we deeply regret
OL,8,Fthe impact this decision will have on
OL,9,Fall our employees, clients and supply
OL,10,Fchain."
OL,12,FThe businesses say they will work with
OL,13,Fliquidators to try and protect these
OL,14,Fgroups' interests during "this
OL,15,Fextremely difficult and distressing
OL,16,Ftime".
