OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FThe collapse of these firms has
OL,7,Fsparked concerns as it comes just a
OL,8,Fyear since fellow construction
OL,9,Fcompanies Camerons and JP Mauger
OL,10,Ffolded.
OL,12,FThe island's Chamber of Commerce says:
OL,13,F"This is another blow for Jersey's
OL,14,Fconstruction industry and further
OL,15,Fevidence, if it was needed, of the
OL,16,Fchallenging conditions the
OL,17,Fconstruction and development sector
OL,18,Fface at present."
