OL,3,CThree construction firms go bust
OL,4,Cleaving 78 people jobless
OL,6,FIt has called on private and public
OL,7,Fsector clients to continue to invest
OL,8,Fin projects to keep the sector afloat.
OL,10,FIt also urged Jersey's government to
OL,11,F"speed up" its future projects and
OL,12,Fhelp local tradespeople with
OL,13,Fopportunities to deliver quality work.
OL,15,FThe Chamber adds: "The sooner these
OL,16,Fprojects can be turned into on-site
OL,17,Factivity, the better the chances of
OL,18,Fthe local industry surviving the
OL,19,Fpresent challenging conditions."
